WEBVTT

00:05.333 --> 00:06.333
Ugh! Gee!

00:06.666 --> 00:07.666
Ugh!

00:09.582 --> 00:11.000
Why's it so hot?

00:16.666 --> 00:18.041
Ahhh!

00:18.541 --> 00:20.000
Oooh-oooh-oooh! Ow!

00:23.541 --> 00:24.541
Ahhhh!

00:25.499 --> 00:26.707
Here it is, hyuck.

00:26.707 --> 00:31.457
The hottest day of the year.
And we're stayin' cool in style!

00:31.707 --> 00:32.749
Yeah!

00:32.749 --> 00:35.291
And we owe it all to you, Mick!

00:35.291 --> 00:37.541
Nothin's too good for my two best pals!

00:37.541 --> 00:39.208
Ohhh!

00:39.208 --> 00:41.749
What are you jerks doin' in my pool?

00:43.083 --> 00:44.124
Sick 'em!

00:50.166 --> 00:51.166
Ooh!

00:57.249 --> 00:58.874
Phew!
That was a close one!

00:58.874 --> 01:01.124
It's a million degrees out here!

01:01.124 --> 01:03.374
Now what're we going to do?!

01:03.374 --> 01:05.707
Take it easy! I said I'd
find us a way to stay cool,

01:05.707 --> 01:06.790
and I will!

01:06.790 --> 01:09.124
Yeah, well you better hurry up.

01:09.124 --> 01:11.416
Goofy's not doing so good.

01:13.874 --> 01:15.208
Huh? Huh?

01:19.666 --> 01:20.749
Splat!

01:25.249 --> 01:26.582
Con-tact!

01:45.957 --> 01:47.582
How bout this heat, huh?

01:48.208 --> 01:49.832
<i>Ahhh!</i>

01:51.124 --> 01:51.790
Grrr!

01:54.166 --> 01:55.416
Fellas!

01:56.374 --> 01:57.374
Grrr!

02:03.790 --> 02:04.790
Woo-hoo!

02:08.957 --> 02:10.208
Huh?

02:17.790 --> 02:19.124
Ahhhh.

02:21.790 --> 02:23.749
Awwwww, momma!

02:25.499 --> 02:26.541
Woo-hey!

02:34.416 --> 02:35.666
Ohhhh.

02:37.333 --> 02:39.166
Ho-ho-ho!
Tee-hee-hee!

02:44.499 --> 02:45.790
Woo!

02:45.790 --> 02:47.832
Hey! Who's driving
this thing anyway?

02:50.832 --> 02:51.874
Ahhh!

03:16.541 --> 03:17.749
Hooray!

03:27.000 --> 03:28.874
Hey, I'm freezing.
